				\usepackage{upgreek}
				\setlength{\oddsidemargin}{-69pt}
				\begin{document}$\sim0.5\text{--}4$\end{document} kHz range (Záhlava et al. 2019), research by Ripoll et al. (2020) shows that typically the whistler power contributed by LGWs is low compared to other sources (amplitudes of ∼1\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
