To recognize the modes in which the waves propagate, the EMFISIS WNA data set contains an SVD estimator of the ellipticity of the magnetic field polarization (see Santolík et al. 2002) obtained from two largest singular values and from the sign of the imaginary component of the cross-spectrum of the two magnetic field components perpendicular to B→0\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
