There have been additional efforts to use the EMFISIS Waves spectrum to determine the electron density. One of them (Zhelavskaya et al. 2016) uses a neural network to identify the upper hybrid frequency in the Waves data. The neural network was trained using previously determined values of fuh\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
